_sText:
AWP map for 36 people.

The map was created specifically for the new year 2019. That is why I released it on January 1. The card itself was made long before this date. And that's why I wasn't the first to publish my version of the map. The map itself is a new look at awp_lego_2. I hope you enjoy this.

CS:GO version: https://gamebanana.com/maps/202940
